data.description: 3BR/2BA home with over 1675 sqft, great schools and convenient to everything! The family room has wood-look tile flooring and fireplace. The kitchen has granite countertops and all appliances remain. Office nook off the kitchen. Bonus/sunroom is off the dining area and leads to the screened back porch. Privacy fenced backyard with grilling area and storage building. Large storage room off the garage.
